title: Amandine Hawaii 2012
description:
"Recently Amandine Sanchez has a bit slow down on contest surfing , however she remains more involved into surfing than ever. Free Surfing, coaching kids from the French team and the BASC, filming and shooting, Amandine knows how to stay busy.
That trip to Hawaii was a good example: Amandine went there to coach Dean an O'Neill grommet for his first trip on the Rock and she still managed to shoot with some photogs and put together that little edit... Enjoy... "
